sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant OAuth as oauth-proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant OAuthServer as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (pod-internal)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS TLS

    Note over Browser,OAuthServer: Flow 1: User Dashboard Access (Initial Authentication)
    Browser->>Router: GET /dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS
    Router->>OAuth: Forward (TLS reencrypt)<br/>HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>OAuthServer: OAuth2 Authorization Flow<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS
    OAuthServer-->>OAuth: Access Token + Session Cookie
    OAuth->>Backend: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080 (plaintext, pod-internal)<br/>Header: x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend-->>OAuth: HTML/JS/CSS (React SPA)
    OAuth-->>Router: Response (TLS)
    Router-->>Browser: Dashboard UI

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Kubernetes API Proxy (e.g., list notebooks)
    Browser->>Router: GET /api/k8s/apis/kubeflow.org/v1/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS + OAuth session cookie
    Router->>OAuth: Forward (TLS reencrypt)
    OAuth->>Backend: /api/k8s/*<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/kubeflow.org/v1/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS<br/>Bearer Token (user's token)
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook list (JSON)
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON response
    OAuth-->>Router: Response (TLS)
    Router-->>Browser: Notebook data

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Query
    Browser->>Router: POST /api/prometheus/query<br/>HTTPS/443 + OAuth session
    Router->>OAuth: Forward (TLS reencrypt)
    OAuth->>Backend: /api/prometheus/query<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>Thanos: POST /api/v1/query<br/>HTTPS/9092 TLS<br/>Bearer Token (user's token)
    Thanos-->>Backend: Metrics data (JSON)
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON response
    OAuth-->>Router: Response (TLS)
    Router-->>Browser: Metrics data

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 4: WebSocket Watch (real-time updates)
    Browser->>Router: WSS /wss/k8s/*<br/>Upgrade: websocket
    Router->>OAuth: Forward WebSocket
    OAuth->>Backend: WS /wss/k8s/*<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Watch API (WebSocket)<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Watch events (streaming)
    Backend-->>Browser: Real-time resource updates
